getAllDocuments().notice: Used to retrieve a full list of documents attached to the smart contract.

returns._0: string List of all documents names present in the contract.

getDocument(string).notice: Used to return the details of a document with a known name (`string`).

returns._0: string The data associated with the document.
returns._1: uint256 the timestamp at which the document was last modified.

getDocumentCount().notice: Used to retrieve the total documents in the smart contract.

returns._0: uint256 Count of the document names present in the contract.

getDocumentName(uint256).notice: Used to retrieve the document name from index in the smart contract.

returns._0: string Name of the document name.
